Ye, it is a new feature since 3.5.0.
Generally, setting
```js
tooltip: {
    axisPointer: {
        type: 'cross'
    }
}
```
is OK to enable it.

If it doesn't work for you, may I have your `option` to diagnose it?

```  javascript
 series: [
            {
                // name: '访问来源',
                type: 'pie',
                selectedMode:'single',//这个很重要，如果不设置，定义要选中关闭，会导致pieselectedchange事件无效
        }
]

```
其实这个不BUG，而是文档没有说明清楚
